      <div class="service-card"><h3>Wood Heater Service</h3><p>Slow combustion heater flue clean and inspection. Baffle check, door seal inspection, full flue swept top to bottom.</p></div>
      <div class="service-card"><h3>Chimney Inspection</h3><p>Visual inspection of firebox, flue, damper, crown and pot. Written report available on request. Included in the $199 service.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REVIEWS -->
  <section class="reviews-section" id="reviews">
    <h2>What Point Cook Customers Say</h2>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;We have a slow combustion heater in our Point Cook estate home that gets used every night through winter. David cleaned the full flue system and found significant creosote build-up. Heater runs much more efficiently now — great service.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Michael B., Point Cook</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;David came out quickly and was very professional. Cleaned the flue from top to bottom and gave a clear verbal report on the condition. No mess, no fuss. Will definitely be calling again next year.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Stephanie L., Point Cook</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Our heater had never had a professional service since it was installed. David found the flue was heavily restricted with creosote and cleared it completely. The improvement in draw and heat output is remarkable.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Raj P., Point Cook</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
