    <h2>About Dave&rsquo;s Chimney Sweeping</h2>
    <p>Dave&rsquo;s Chimney Sweeping is a local, owner-operated business covering Melbourne's western suburbs including Point Cook. Dave personally handles every job &mdash; no subcontractors, no call centres. Flat $199 rate per chimney, no hidden fees.</p>
    <a class="btn-secondary" href="tel:0476302729">Call Dave — 0476 302 729</a>
  </section>

